nodes.text: Jess was a group of Freighters belonging to the Habassa. Jess 6, 7, and 8 were all operated by the Habassan convoy that was attacked by Assault Gunboats. Keyan Farlander came to their aid in a B-wing. Jess 6 was disabled by the Imperials and was attempted to be looted by Slick, an Imperial freighter, but it was destroyed. Jess 9 hypered in with some Y-wings and saved the crew. Keyan was successful in stopping the attack.
